(17, 1, '2017-10-30 23:09:54', '2017-10-30 23:09:54', 'Fujifilm Prescale is a unique, affordable and easy to use tool that reveals the distribution and magnitude of pressure between any two contacting, mating or impacting surfaces. This Tactile Pressure Indicating Sensor Film is extremely thin (4 to 8 mils) which enables it to conform to curved surfaces. Fuji Prescale Film is ideal for invasive intolerant environments and tight spaces not accessible to conventional electronic transducers.', 'Fujifilm Prescale', 'https://youtu.be/3hLmmEWLF-Y\r\n\r\nReveals the distribution and magnitude of pressure between any two contacting, mating or impacting surfaces.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'fujifilm-prescale', '', '', '2017-11-14 01:43:52', '2017-11-14 01:43:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost:90/wordpress/product/orange-tree-3/', 0, 'product', '', 1),
